{
  "stem": "20609.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "So every day, he used to come to the stable.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And sometimes he used to come early inspecting.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "We had to clean all the horses and you scraped them with that scraper and a brush.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And then you hit the brush on the cement floor and then you had to have like 10 lines.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And if you didn't have 10 lines, you were in trouble.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "So you really, really had to clean the horse.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "You couldn't take those lines away till about 11, 12 o'clock, you know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "But basically, because we had an old fashioned sergeant, a Jewish guy who was a Sergeant in the Czechoslovakian cavalry, he was in charge of the stables.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he also took care of Commandant [INAUDIBLE] horse, which he almost rode every day.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So that means every day we saw the lousy commandant.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That means we never know what the son of a bitch was going to do, right?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because these people are unpredictable and there's-- let's be realistic about it, they had open season.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, they could kill you.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They don't even have to put a report in.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Why did you kill him?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Right?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So nothing.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So-- but our jobs were good, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We had-- we went out with the horses, we picked up the people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And on one day when I pick up the-- pick up the dead bodies, I see a couple of nurses.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I says, why are you here?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Says, well, Professor so-and-so is died.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "That was the same professor who gave me the last shot of serum he had.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And that-- because I never-- I-- I never was interested in who was there, you know.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was just to meet another load I had to bring over and deliver and-- and go back.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
